            "title": "No Department Of Education? What It Means For Municipal Bonds",
            "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Municipal bonds is shown on the business photo using the text\" data-id=\"1350489578\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1350489578/image_1350489578.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Dodonov</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Eliminating the DOE will have little impact on municipal bonds, as schools rely mostly on state and local funding, though short-term disruptions in grants and student loans are possible.</p> <p>We believe the elimination of the federal Department</p>",
